# Link Test

This is a paragraph with several types of formatting:

- Regular link: [Example link](https://www.example.com)
- Text with **bold** and *italics*
- Text with ==highlight== and ~~strikethrough~~
- Another link: [Google](https://www.google.com)

Are the links clearly visible?

